items.Aetherhaven_Plot_Token_Barn_Hytiny.name=Hytiny's barn plot token
items.Aetherhaven_Plot_Token_Barn_Hytiny.description=Marks where the compact Hytiny barn prefab can be built. Prefab by HytinyBuilds. Not sold at the planning desk.
items.Aetherhaven_Plot_Token_House_Hytiny_Cozy_Cottage.name=Hytiny's cozy cottage plot token
items.Aetherhaven_Plot_Token_House_Hytiny_Cozy_Cottage.description=Marks where Hytiny's cozy cottage can be built. Prefab by HytinyBuilds. Craft at the town planning desk.
