items.Aetherhaven_Plot_Token_House_Hytiny_Cozy_Camper.description=Marks where Hytiny's cozy camper can be built. Prefab by HytinyBuilds. Craft at the town planning desk.
items.Aetherhaven_Plot_Token_Decoration_Hytiny_Potted_Treehouse.name=Hytiny's potted treehouse plot token
items.Aetherhaven_Plot_Token_Decoration_Hytiny_Potted_Treehouse.description=<color is="#e53935">Warning: this is a very large prefab and may noticeably slow down or hitch the client and server while it assembles. Place it when you have time to let it finish.</color> Marks where Hytiny's potted treehouse can be built (decorative only). Prefab by HytinyBuilds. Not sold at the planning desk.

items.Aetherhaven_Plot_Token_Gaia_Altar.name=Gaia altar plot token
